comments: Lillard (MIL) avoids making body contact with Shamet (WAS) as he contests the jump shot attempt.
Kuzma (WAS) initiates more than marginal body contact with Lopez (MIL) during his shot attempt near the rim.
Beasley (MIL) contests Jones' (WAS) jump shot attempt and makes clean contact with the ball prior to any incidental "high-five" contact occurring after the release.
Gafford (WAS) and Lopez (MIL) mutually come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal arm contact occurs during the rebound.
Poole (WAS) extends a leg into Lillard (MIL), causing him to trip.
Beasley (MIL) places his hand on Jones' (WAS) side with extension, affecting his SQBR during the driving shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) hooks his left arm around Kuzma's (WAS) arm and initiates illegal contact as the post entry pass is made.
Kuzma (WAS) is not established in a legal guarding position in Lillard's (MIL) path when contact occurs and the contact affects Lillard's shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) swipes down and initiates illegal contact with Shamet's (WAS) arm during his shot attempt at the rim.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) and Shamet (WAS) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) attempts to cut off the baseline and marginal leg contact occurs with Poole (WAS).
Lillard (MIL) stops short as Shamet (WAS) defends him during the throw-in, but the contact is marginal and Lillard is not dislodged from his position as a result of the contact.
Kispert (WAS) commits a take foul on Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Kispert (WAS) commits a take foul on Connaughton (MIL).
Shamet (WAS) commits a take foul on Lillard (MIL).
Lillard (MIL) legally contests Kuzma's (WAS) jump shot attempt.
